
0.9.0
- Added placing objects
- Fixed obstacle layer disappearing when resizing map

0.8.1
- Added second map layer
- Fixed bug in creating a new map

0.8.0
- You can specify tilesets to be automatically imported in the configuration file
- Added selected color display and Saturation and Value color sliders.
- Fixed bug in tileset window that showed up when giving it another size.
- A few changes have been made to get MingW to compile the source (linking still gives errors).
- Added a makefile for easy compilation without MSVC.
- Fixed potential memory corruption with edit fields.
- Added "Resize map..." functionality.
- About box centering fixed.
